sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant U as Developer
    participant RFE as rfe-creator
    participant JIRA as Jira RHAIRFE/RHAISTRAT
    participant TP as test-plan-creator
    participant TR as test-rules-generator
    participant AGENT as Claude Code Agent
    participant REPO as Component Repo

    rect rgb(26, 26, 46)
    Note over U, JIRA: Phase 1-2: RFE + Strategy Pipeline
    U->>RFE: /rfe.speedrun "problem statement"
    RFE->>RFE: create → review → auto-revise
    RFE->>JIRA: Submit RHAIRFE ticket
    JIRA-->>RFE: RHAIRFE-1595
    RFE->>RFE: /strat.create RHAIRFE-1595
    RFE->>RFE: /strat.refine → /strat.review
    RFE->>JIRA: Submit RHAISTRAT ticket
    JIRA-->>RFE: RHAISTRAT-400
    RFE-->>U: Strategy refined + submitted
    end

    rect rgb(26, 46, 26)
    Note over U, REPO: Phase 3-4: Test Planning + Rules (parallel)
    par Test Plan Generation
        U->>TP: /test-plan-creator RHAISTRAT-400
        TP->>JIRA: Fetch strategy details
        JIRA-->>TP: Strategy + linked RFE content
        TP->>TP: Fork: scope + strategy + environment analyzers
        TP->>TP: Merge → TestPlan.md
        TP->>TP: /test-plan-reviewer validates
        TP-->>U: feature_name/TestPlan.md
    and Test Rules Extraction
        U->>TR: /test-rules-generator repo-url
        TR->>REPO: Clone + analyze test patterns
        REPO-->>TR: Test files + frameworks
        TR->>TR: Extract patterns per test type
        TR-->>U: .claude/rules/*.md
    end
    end

    rect rgb(46, 26, 46)
    Note over AGENT, REPO: Phase 5: Agent Writes Tests
    U->>AGENT: "Write tests for this feature"
    AGENT->>AGENT: Read TestPlan.md (what to test)
    AGENT->>AGENT: Read .claude/rules/*.md (how to test)
    AGENT->>REPO: Generate test files following patterns
    AGENT->>AGENT: Run tests, validate coverage
    AGENT-->>U: Test cases + coverage report
    end
